Doctolib’s Engineering environment is rich and we are building innovative products and features aiming each day to ease doctors' and patient life.

We are looking for our next Engineering Manager - AI to join our tech domains in Berlin. You will join a team of hard working entrepreneurs, who are passionate about transforming healthcare and play an active role in shaping a fast-growing company from day one!

To go beyond the ad, please check our technical blog!

